{{Year nav topic5|2008|rugby union}} Here are the match results of the 2008 [[Rugby union]] season. Qualifiers for the [[2011 Rugby World Cup]] began in the [[Caribbean]], meanwhile the [[Six Nations Championship]] and the [[Tri Nations (rugby union)|Tri Nations]] are set for another season.
