{{Infobox Sport governing body |assocname= Fédération Québecoise des Sports Cyclistes |abbrev = FQSC |logo=Logo of the FQSC.jpg |sport=[[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] |founded = |aff =[[Canadian Cycling Association]] |affdate = |region = |regionyear = | image = | image_border = | size = | caption = | category = | jurisdiction = | year formed = | headquarters = | president = | chairman = | key staff = |chiefexec = |replaced = |prevfounded = |url =www.fqsc.net/ |countryflag= Quebec |countryflag2= }}
'''Fédération Québecoise des Sports Cyclistes''' or '''FQSC''' (the '''Quebec Cycling Federation''') is the provincial [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Quebec]], [[Canada]].
The national governing body for Canada is the [[Canadian Cycling Association]].
