{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2015}} {{Infobox sportsperson | name = Gilbert Scorsoglio | birth_name = | fullname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1932|7|21|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Monaco]] | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | website = | country = | sport = [[Shooting sport|Sports shooting]] | event = | medaltemplates = | show-medals = yes }}
'''Gilbert Scorsoglio''' (born 21 July 1932) is a [[Monaco|Monegasque]] former [[Shooting sport|sports shooter]]. He competed at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]] and the [[1968 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/sc/gilbert-scorsoglio-1.html |title=Gilbert Scorsoglio |accessdate=4 July 2015 |work=Sports Reference |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613014556/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/sc/gilbert-scorsoglio-1.html |archivedate=13 June 2015 |df=dmy }}</ref>
