{{Infobox national handball team | Name = Luxembourg | Badge = Fédération Luxembourgeoise de Handball.jpg | Badge_size = 150px | Nickname = | Association = Fédération Luxembourgeoise de Handball | Coach = Adrian Stot | Most caps = | Most goals = }} The '''Luxembourg national handball team''' is the national team of [[Luxembourg]]. It takes part in international [[handball]] competitions.
The team participated at the [[1958 World Men's Handball Championship]], where they placed 16th.
