The '''Rwanda Davis Cup team''' represents [[Rwanda]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Rwandaise de Tennis]]. They have not competed since [[2013 Davis Cup|2013]].
Rwanda currently compete in the Europe/Africa Zone of Group III. They finished second in Group B of Group IV in [[2005 Davis Cup|2005]].
==History== Rwanda competed in its first Davis Cup in [[2001 Davis Cup|2001]].
